<h3>
<a name="savedpass"></a>Every time I go to your site I have an incorrect password already
            in the password text box. How do I remove a saved password?</h3>
<p> To clear stored passwords in Internet Explorer for Windows, follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
<li>Open Internet Explorer. </li>
<li>Click on Tools, and select Internet Options. </li>
<li>Click on the Content tab. </li>
<li>Click on the Auto Complete button. </li>
<li>Click Clear Passwords. </li>
</ol>
